Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:10:01.03,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Welcome to ProSeka AfterTalk "Kimi to Tsunagu Heart Beat" Edition!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:04.74,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Hello everyone! {\i1}Kon-needo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:07.74,Ichika,,0,0,0,,This is Ruriko Noguchi, voice of Ichika Hoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:10.37,Ichika,,0,0,0,,In these ProSeka Aftertalks,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:15.84,Ichika,,0,0,0,,we'll look back at this event while covering messages you, the fans, have sent in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:19.97,Ichika,,0,0,0,,This time, we'll be covering the "Kimi to Tsunagu Heart Beat" event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:24.12,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Did you like the story, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:28.25,Ichika,,0,0,0,,The story this time was a pretty happy one, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:31.48,Ichika,,0,0,0,,When I first read the script ,I was like "is it really okay for so many good things to happen?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:35.37,Ichika,,0,0,0,,So many good things. I was really happy going through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:41.27,Ichika,,0,0,0,,This story made me realize the warmth and importance of bonds between people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:45.48,Ichika,,0,0,0,,We'll go more in depth in the story later, so please stay tuned for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:49.58,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Also, Aftertalks have had a bit of a mini-renewal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:55.27,Ichika,,0,0,0,,We've gathered your comments for this Aftertalk sent through email as well as the submissions channel on the Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:57.63,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Thanks for all the messages everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:11:01.07,Ichika,,0,0,0,,We'd like to go over some of them in our program today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:02.92,Ichika,,0,0,0,,so please look forward to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:05.38,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Also, if you have any thoughts on today's program,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:08.91,Ichika,,0,0,0,,please post them on X with #ProSekaAftertalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:11.19,Ichika,,0,0,0,,We'll also be watching the YouTube chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:13.89,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Please keep all the messages coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:17.19,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Already seeing lots of {\i1}"Kon-needo!"{\i0} Thanks everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:18.69,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"I just finished the story!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:22.81,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Thanks for rushing to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:26.57,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Right then, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:33.61,Ichika,,0,0,0,,We'll start by talking about the "Kimi to Tsunagu Heart Beat" story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:36.85,Ichika,,0,0,0,,What did you think of the story, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:40.78,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Let's look back together while going over some of the messages you've sent in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:44.19,Ichika,,0,0,0,,First up, a message from "Misora"-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:46.20,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"Good evening, Noguchi-san!" Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:48.62,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"Thanks as always for providing us with a wonderful voice for Ichika."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:50.15,Ichika,,0,0,0,,The pleasure is all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:57.27,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"I loved seeing Ichika-chan pour her all of her love for Miku into a new song in this story."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:12:00.58,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"I couldn't stop smiling and feeling warm inside."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:04.70,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"But that last serious look from Shiho-chan also has me a bit curious."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:08.68,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"Regardless, I'm just happy that Ichika-chan is so happy."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:12.16,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your comments, Misora-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:18.52,Ichika,,0,0,0,,So this time, Ichika wrote a new song "with" around the theme of "What Miku means to me",
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:23.67,Ichika,,0,0,0,,putting in feelings of everything she's been through with Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:29.22,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Then when she uploaded it, that creator Aoi-san reacted out her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:35.64,Ichika,,0,0,0,,asking to make an MV together. It got so many views and just kept blowing up from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:42.65,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I mentioned this at the beginning, but I just kept thinking "wow, is it really okay for everything to work out this well?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:46.49,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Just so many good things happening for Ichika in this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:55.58,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I'm really glad that Ichika was able to accomplish one of her goals of connecting people through music.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.77,Ichika,,0,0,0,,It may be just a small first step for now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:13:01.57,Ichika,,0,0,0,,but I really think is a story where one of her wishes came true,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:08.46,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help but have a huge smile the whole time I was playing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:14.20,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, and they mentioned that last scene with Shiho's serious look...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:15.66,Ichika,,0,0,0,,what do you think of that, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:17.75,Ichika,,0,0,0,,How did that make you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:19.61,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Shiho— she—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:23.94,Ichika,,0,0,0,,she said that she was really happy for Ichika at the end there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.51,Ichika,,0,0,0,,but to me, it looked a little like,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:29.70,Ichika,,0,0,0,,yeah... she definitely looked like something was on her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:33.67,Ichika,,0,0,0,,You know, we haven't really seen Shiho like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:37.82,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I can't help wondering what's making her feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:40.06,Ichika,,0,0,0,,But yeah, Shiho-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:43.27,Ichika,,0,0,0,,her being so serious about this band—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:46.66,Ichika,,0,0,0,,everyone is, but amidst all that Ichika,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:50.13,Ichika,,0,0,0,,yeah, making Miku songs on her own,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.13,0:13:53.81,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Shiho has any feelings about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:56.73,Ichika,,0,0,0,,And I wonder what kind of story that will lead to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:58.91,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Even I have no idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:13:59.80,Ichika,,0,0,0,,buuuuuuut,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:03.04,Ichika,,0,0,0,,maybe that's just how bands are, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:04.76,Ichika,,0,0,0,,But, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:10.45,Ichika,,0,0,0,,there are plenty of folks who make Miku songs solo but are also part of bands, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:19.63,Ichika,,0,0,0,,So I hope that Ichika can also do that and continue pursuing her happiness further.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:23.75,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I just hope that she can continue doing her best as part of Leo/need,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:27.35,Ichika,,0,0,0,,and that she can continue creating songs with her beloved Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:33.01,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what the future holds for her, but let's keep watching over her warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:37.90,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Alright. Now let's move on to the next message.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:41.26,Ichika,,0,0,0,,A message from "YMMK"-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:43.30,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"Noguchi-san, {\i1}kon-needo{\i0}!" {\i1}Kon-needo{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:51.39,Ichika,,0,0,0,,In this event story, Ichika composed a song "with", pouring her feelings for Miku into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:56.12,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"but it seemed like Ichika wasn't really thinking about what to do after she finished it."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:56.91,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:15:02.22,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"There was a scene where she seemed happy just to show the completed song to the rest of Leo/need."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:07.35,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"Noguchi-san, are there any times where you also felt satisfied just by doing the task itself?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:09.61,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:14.74,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Right, Saki-chan was the one who actually suggested uploading the song after Ichika show it to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:17.93,Ichika,,0,0,0,,But yeah, "things I feel satisfied just by doing"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.43,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:22.61,Ichika,,0,0,0,,The other day, I tried making curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:25.03,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I just felt like trying making it one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:29.73,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I did feel satisfied doing it... but it was annoying to eat all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:32.74,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I made so many portions!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:33.58,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:36.05,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I made way too many portions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:37.70,Ichika,,0,0,0,,But it's like,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:39.89,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I really was proud of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:41.50,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I was happy with what I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:46.31,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I feel like eating food you cooked yourself doesn't really have the same allure, does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:48.40,Ichika,,0,0,0,,You just cook stuff, then eat it normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:52.63,Ichika,,0,0,0,,You do it just for the sense of accomplishment, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:55.37,Ichika,,0,0,0,,This is kind of unrelated,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:59.09,Ichika,,0,0,0,,but I don't actually have a knife in my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.09,0:15:59.98,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I'm not even sure how.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:01.80,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I definitely did have one before. I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:04.91,Ichika,,0,0,0,,But somehow it suddenly vanished. Isn't that scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:08.99,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I needed to cut some carrots, but I couldn't without a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.99,0:16:11.87,Ichika,,0,0,0,,So I ended up cutting them with scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:16.10,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I had to cut them like "{\i1}krhhhh{\i0}."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:18.11,Ichika,,0,0,0,,That was really satisfying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:21.06,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Putting in the work to cut the carrots like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:25.01,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I thought I wouldn't even have enough energy left to eat what I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:27.94,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Just kidding. I did end up eat all of it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:29.61,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:30.87,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Was was I talking about again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:32.57,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I completely forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:35.05,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:36.43,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Let's get back on track.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:41.80,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I've selected some of my favorite scenes from the story for today, so let's watch them together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:43.66,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Comment: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:47.80,Note,,0,0,0,,------BEGIN STORY------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.37,0:22:43.65,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Hmm. That's a very Ichika way of thinking.
Comment: 0,0:25:08.58,0:25:10.30,Ichika,,0,0,0,,------END STORY------
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.09,0:25:10.30,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the video. That was Chapter 8 of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.30,0:25:14.02,Ichika,,0,0,0,,So as for why I chose this particular scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.02,0:25:19.87,Ichika,,0,0,0,,when Shiho asks Ichika about the song she put so much of her own feelings into going viral,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.87,0:25:23.87,Ichika,,0,0,0,,and if she was bothered by strangers creating covers and their own works form it,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.87,0:25:28.62,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I thought it was interesting how Ichika says "no, I'm actually really glad."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.62,0:25:34.09,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Maybe some creators out there say things like "this is how many song should be,"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.09,0:25:35.41,Ichika,,0,0,0,,but Ichika isn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.41,0:25:44.37,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Instead she thinks "it's awesome that my song is helping connect many different people"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.37,0:25:48.41,Ichika,,0,0,0,,That's a sign of how strong and wonderful she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.41,0:25:53.40,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I see everyone's saying that they're a bit restless.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.40,0:25:56.99,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Yep, does looks like everyone has lots of thoughts on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.99,0:26:01.22,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Saki-chan— like some of you mentioned—
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.22,0:26:04.68,Ichika,,0,0,0,,really likes being close with fans on a personal level,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.68,0:26:09.61,Ichika,,0,0,0,,while we see Ichika's seems to enjoy her music spreading to all sorts of places,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.61,0:26:14.02,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Everyone in Leo/need seems to have their own desires...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.02,0:26:18.44,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I do wonder a bit on how things will play out going forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.44,0:26:26.18,Ichika,,0,0,0,,but having the song she created out of her feelings for Miku spreading so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.18,0:26:29.59,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Ichika must be so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.59,0:26:32.22,Ichika,,0,0,0,,This is supposed to be a happy story,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.22,0:26:37.49,Ichika,,0,0,0,,so I just hope Ichika is able to continue creating songs like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.49,0:26:41.16,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the comments, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.16,0:26:43.10,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"What's gonna happen?"—
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.10,0:26:43.69,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.69,0:26:47.03,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Someone says "their musical direction is drifting apart."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.03,0:26:49.48,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Will something come of that? I don't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.48,0:26:52.03,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's gonna happen next...
Comment: 0,0:26:52.03,0:26:52.89,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Timing is really weird on the line below somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.89,0:26:57.08,Ichika,,0,0,0,,But at least things are still happy for now, so let's please leave it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.08,0:27:00.20,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Not yet, not yet. We don't know what's coming next.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.20,0:27:04.86,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Really guys, I don't know what's next either. I just want to see Ichika happy like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.86,0:27:11.50,Ichika,,0,0,0,,As the one playing her, I just want her to keep doing what makes her happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.50,0:27:15.10,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I'm just praying that things work out for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.10,0:27:19.42,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Anyway, thanks for looking through the comments with me.
Comment: 0,0:27:15.10,0:27:15.10,Ichika,,0,0,0,,-------END STORY TALK------
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.42,0:27:22.26,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Alright, then, moving on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.26,0:27:25.93,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look at the card art together.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.93,0:27:31.22,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Let's bring up the card art.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.31,0:27:38.98,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}I, uh, named my team "Ichi" this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.98,0:27:40.58,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Starting off with Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.14,0:27:43.78,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.50,0:27:46.79,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}This is the trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.79,0:27:50.13,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Isn't this so cute though?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.13,0:27:53.32,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Ichika's in front leading the parade,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.32,0:27:55.32,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}and I think those are like comments?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.32,0:28:01.33,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}It's so cute seeing so many comments about her song in the art like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.33,0:28:03.99,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}You can tell she's having so much fun, I just love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.99,0:28:07.88,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Oh yeah, and it looks like the outfits have a red motif this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.88,0:28:09.99,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}I feel like that gives the art good impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.99,0:28:12.09,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Just super cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.09,0:28:14.24,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,These comments are also really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.24,0:28:16.61,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Listeners saying "this song helps me do my best!"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.61,0:28:19.37,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Really really cute,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.37,0:28:22.79,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,I want this as a a huge poster in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.79,0:28:24.20,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Just so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.20,0:28:27.14,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Let's check out the untrained too.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.14,0:28:29.45,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Wow, really surprised, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.45,0:28:33.88,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,This should be from the scene where she sees the message from Aoi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.88,0:28:36.88,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Glad we get to see her cactus too.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.88,0:28:40.22,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,And it's super cute seeing her in her futon like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.22,0:28:45.05,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,It must be really surprising getting a DM from one of your favorite creators like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.05,0:28:47.28,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,She's probably like "woah, what is it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.28,0:28:53.16,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Super glad the DM ended up being such a great thing for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.16,0:28:55.75,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Even her ordinary life makes a great shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.75,0:28:56.86,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Moving on to Hona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.04,0:28:58.94,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.65,0:29:01.30,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Super cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.30,0:29:02.95,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Love her wink.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.95,0:29:06.57,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Her hair matches the outfit color really well,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.57,0:29:09.10,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,it looks so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.10,0:29:11.95,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,And her drum is really colorful too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.95,0:29:13.98,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Super cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.98,0:29:15.45,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,This card is go good...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.45,0:29:17.84,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,And the backdrop is really pretty too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.84,0:29:21.80,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Seeing all the commenters in the background there is also super cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.15,0:29:25.06,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Love it. Let's move onto the untrained then.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.06,0:29:26.73,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.73,0:29:30.61,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Way too cuuuuuute~{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.61,0:29:32.35,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,It's lil bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.35,0:29:33.98,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,And Shibao's back there too— ahhh too cute~
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.98,0:29:36.22,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Gotta look for every detail here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.22,0:29:38.97,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.97,0:29:42.45,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Having siblings must be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.45,0:29:44.33,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Super cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.33,0:29:45.94,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Haru-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.94,0:29:47.35,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,"Everyone was talking about this!" Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.35,0:29:48.89,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,That also surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.89,0:29:50.40,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Didn't realize he was so cute too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.40,0:29:52.54,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Was not expecting that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.54,0:29:55.18,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Haru-kun's really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.18,0:29:58.28,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,I hope we get to see more of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.28,0:29:59.75,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,"He's so cute." 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.75,0:30:04.61,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,"Seeing this little slice of life is really nice." Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.61,0:30:06.92,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,And Honami is cooking, naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.92,0:30:09.20,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Hona-chan would definitely use an actual knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.19,0:30:14.34,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Alright, here's Shiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.34,0:30:15.86,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,SO COOL!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.86,0:30:17.24,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Shiho~
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.24,0:30:20.24,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,I love how it looks like she's getting ready to take on the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.24,0:30:22.91,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,It screams Shiho, I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.91,0:30:25.91,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,She looks so ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.91,0:30:29.71,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Ah, what's gonna happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.04,0:30:34.13,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Man, I just hope everything turns out well for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.13,0:30:37.84,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,The red pants look super cool on Shiho though.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.53,0:30:40.41,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.41,0:30:43.60,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Someone says "very ikemen". Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.60,0:30:46.91,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,So cool. Cute and cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.91,0:30:49.43,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,So good. Love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.43,0:30:51.93,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Ah. The untrained.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.93,0:30:55.79,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Tuning her bass. 
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.79,0:31:01.64,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,Wonder if all bassists look this cool when they tune.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.64,0:31:04.51,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.51,0:31:07.64,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,The classroom looks nice with the 
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.90,0:32:55.38,Ichika - PiP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,750)}Also, be sure to check out all the detail in the colors.
Comment: 0,0:32:55.38,0:32:55.38,Note,,0,0,0,,~~~Card Talk end~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.38,0:32:55.82,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Moving on,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.82,0:33:01.55,Ichika,,0,0,0,,this event's commissioned song was "Star", composed by Daibakuhasin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.55,0:33:06.05,Ichika,,0,0,0,,We'll watch the MV together and talk a little bit about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.05,0:33:12.55,Ichika,,0,0,0,,But first, we actually have a comment from SEGA's 3DMV production team.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.55,0:33:14.54,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Let's read it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.54,0:33:18.70,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"For Star's MV, we took strong inspiration for the song itself,"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.70,0:33:23.56,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"and wanted to convey the fun and excitement Ichika has creating music and seeing it reach so many,"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.56,0:33:28.16,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"while also keeping Leo/need at the center."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.16,0:33:33.49,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"Some of our favorite scenes were Leo/need having fun together during down time at the studio,"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.49,0:33:36.17,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"and the scene where they walk out on stage together."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.17,0:33:43.31,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"We put lots of attention to detail into everyone's expressions to show the fun Leo/need have in their daily lives."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.31,0:33:48.69,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"We hope you enjoy seeing a side of Leo/need's lives that haven't been shown in past MVs."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.88,0:33:53.45,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"Furthermore, while Leo/need already has many MVs where they before under a blue sky, "
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.45,0:33:58.66,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"this time, we showed the gradation in a sky transitioning from night to day."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.66,0:34:02.53,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"Holding close those feelings of a clear and pleasant sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.53,0:34:08.98,Ichika,,0,0,0,,we aimed to paint a picture of the girls' hope for a bright and cloudless future."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.98,0:34:13.04,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"We hope you enjoy this MV along with the song."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.04,0:34:14.20,Ichika,,0,0,0,,That was the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.20,0:34:17.83,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Now let's watch the MV together.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.83,0:34:18.92,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Comment: 0,0:36:06.99,0:36:06.99,Ichika,,0,0,0,,-------BEGIN SONG TALK------
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.03,0:36:14.90,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,That was the 3DMV for Star, thanks for watching along, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.90,0:36:20.10,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,As the production team mentioned, we got to see lots of slice of life shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.10,0:36:23.80,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,Like when they're about to walk out on stage, didn't that just hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.80,0:36:27.26,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,Felt like there were lots of scenes we haven't really seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.26,0:36:29.25,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,And the sky was really pretty too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.25,0:36:31.66,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,So sparkly and bright, it looked incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.66,0:36:34.92,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,And that selfie part with everyone was also super cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.92,0:36:36.24,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,So beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.24,0:36:40.18,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,I feel like, haven't the recent 3DMVs been amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.18,0:36:42.12,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,Thank you staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.12,0:36:45.81,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,Speaking of the song itself, there're a lot of "la la la"s—
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.81,0:36:49.70,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,Opening the song with the "la lala la"s was pretty impactful.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.70,0:36:53.44,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,Thought I was gonna run out of breath during the recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.44,0:37:02.52,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,But seeing all that excitement and passion Ichika has for songwriting and Miku...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.52,0:37:04.77,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,Of course, she might have her uncertainties,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.77,0:37:10.58,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,but she also has this willingness to just keep move forward and enjoying herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.58,0:37:13.58,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,I tried to highlight all of that during the recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.58,0:37:15.98,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,And the lyrics too... they just fit so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.98,0:37:18.99,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,Isn't it like that every time? I'm always thinking like,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.99,0:37:22.23,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,"how do the lyrics fit the story so well every single time?" 
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.23,0:37:24.00,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,They make me so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.00,0:37:28.78,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,Like she might be a little nervous on where things are going to go from here,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.78,0:37:34.19,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,but she's still excited and ready to move forward to whatever's next.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.19,0:37:35.75,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,It's super good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.75,0:37:40.01,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,"Feels like they'd sing the 'la la la's together with everyone at concerts."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.01,0:37:41.98,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,Go for it, everyone. Do you wanna try?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.98,0:37:44.26,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,Let's do the 'la la la's together.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.26,0:37:48.28,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,I think that'd be really nice. Would be a dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.28,0:37:50.54,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,"The lyrics are so good." 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.54,0:37:54.79,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,Ah yeah, the full size is already on YouTube.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.79,0:37:56.09,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,I already watched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.09,0:37:59.27,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,Uh, make sure to watch the 2nd prechorus.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.27,0:38:01.29,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,The energy just skyrockets there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.29,0:38:04.62,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,For Ichika's part when she says "let's begin",
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.62,0:38:09.36,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,I made sure to pump up the excitement there like "oh yeah, let's do this!"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.36,0:38:13.55,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,So please do watch the full version MV.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.55,0:38:16.08,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,Ah— "I'll sing along!" "100% I'll sing along!"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.08,0:38:18.85,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,Everyone's so ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.85,0:38:22.46,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,We're gonna have so much fun, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.46,0:38:26.89,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,Maybe one day, we'll get a chance to sing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.89,0:38:29.11,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank you. "Icchan is so cool in this song!"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.11,0:38:32.69,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,"That part before the 2nd chorus is amazing." Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.69,0:38:35.05,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,So actually, during the recording I thought to myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.05,0:38:39.74,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,"this feels like the climax", so I really belted it for that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.74,0:38:42.17,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you all thought it sounded so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.17,0:38:47.51,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,Ah— someone says "the power's on the same level as Regulus uohhh." Thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.51,0:38:48.38,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,It's good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.38,0:38:52.98,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,The short version is obviously still great, but if you listen to the full version,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.98,0:38:56.59,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,you can experience even more of this wonderful song.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.59,0:39:00.65,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,And the 2D and 3D MVs are already uploaded on the official ProSeka YouTube,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.65,0:39:04.57,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,so do make sure to check them both out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.57,0:39:07.72,Ichika - Song,,0,0,0,,Well then, it was just a short one this time,
Comment: 0,0:39:07.72,0:39:07.72,Note,,0,0,0,,~~~~VIDEO ENDS~~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.72,0:39:12.89,Ichika,,0,0,0,,but that's all we have for the "Kimi to Tsunagu Heart Beat" Aftertalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.89,0:39:16.17,Ichika,,0,0,0,,What did you think about today's episode?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.17,0:39:20.61,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Actually, I just noticed it's been a really long time since the last Aftertalk for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.61,0:39:22.38,Ichika,,0,0,0,,First time since the mini-renewal too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.38,0:39:25.98,Ichika,,0,0,0,,And for the last Ichika focus event, Shiho-chan—
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.98,0:39:29.57,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan was also there, so it's been a while since I've done this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.57,0:39:33.94,Ichika,,0,0,0,,But being able to see everyone's comments in real time,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.94,0:39:39.51,Ichika,,0,0,0,,This is our only chance to really chat together like this, so I'm really glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.51,0:39:41.26,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"Thank you!" "Fun stream!" "Too soon!"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.26,0:39:44.79,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"I'm so glad!" "I always look forward to the Aftertalks."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.79,0:39:48.86,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Actually, the Thanks Festival was just the day before yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.86,0:39:53.51,Ichika,,0,0,0,,so seeing everyone there, and then hearing from everyone here,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.51,0:39:55.62,Ichika,,0,0,0,,so it's full speed ProSeka for me recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.62,0:39:58.76,Ichika,,0,0,0,,But it's been a really fun week.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.76,0:40:00.10,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Week? Was it a week?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.10,0:40:05.66,Ichika,,0,0,0,,We actually also have the Stage Greeting for the movie this coming weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.66,0:40:10.07,Ichika,,0,0,0,,So lots I'm chances to see everyone this week, I'm really glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.07,0:40:14.82,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I hope everyone continues to enjoy everything we have coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.82,0:40:17.55,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Ah, "thanks for the Thanks Festival!" "The Thanks Festival was awesome!"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.55,0:40:18.22,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.22,0:40:19.42,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.42,0:40:23.21,Ichika,,0,0,0,,And thanks to everyone who watched the live viewings or the stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.21,0:40:27.31,Ichika,,0,0,0,,I really do get a lot of energy from all your support,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.31,0:40:29.20,Ichika,,0,0,0,,and I'm looking forward to continuing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.20,0:40:30.64,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.64,0:40:33.42,Ichika,,0,0,0,,So with that, if you haven't watched the "Hoshi wo Tsunagu—"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.42,0:40:37.05,Ichika,,0,0,0,,"Kimi to Tsunagu Heart Beat"  event story yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.05,0:40:42.40,Ichika,,0,0,0,,you can still read it in-game in the "Event Story" section under the "Story" tab, so please do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.40,0:40:45.64,Ichika,,0,0,0,,We'll be accepting submissions for future Aftertalks as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.64,0:40:53.93,Ichika,,0,0,0,,You can submit your messages in the submissions channel on the official Project Sekai Discord, or through email.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.93,0:40:57.98,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Feel free to send them in after the next event starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.98,0:41:02.06,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Please keep your messages related to the events.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.06,0:41:05.76,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Well, that's all for our short time today! Thank you everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.76,0:41:08.56,Ichika,,0,0,0,,See you again next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.56,0:41:13.98,Ichika,,0,0,0,,Bye bye! Thank you! Good night~
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.98,0:41:16.98,Ichika,,0,0,0,,
